---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Semipermanent Makeup – Bliss Dermacare" description="Professional semipermanent makeup at Bliss Dermacare: Nano Brows, Powder Brows, Lip Blush, Lip Neutralization, Scalp Micropigmentation & Custom SPMU in Tampa, FL.">

  <section class="py-14 bg-[#faf9f7] border-b border-neutral-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-4">
        <a href="/services/" class="hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">All Services</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <span class="text-neutral-900 font-medium">Semipermanent Makeup</span>
      </div>
      <span class="text-primary-600 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs font-semibold mb-4 block">Long-Lasting Beauty</span>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-4">Semipermanent Makeup</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 max-w-xl mx-auto">Wake up flawless every day. Precision pigmentation that lasts 1–3 years with proper aftercare. Each service is a standalone booking.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300">
          <div class="relative h-52 overflow-hidden"><img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/23532307/pexels-photo-23532307.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600" alt="Scalp micropigmentation SMP hair follicle impression treatment" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div></div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-2">Scalp Micropigmentation</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">Replicate the look of natural hair follicles for a shaved-head look or to camouflage thinning areas. Non-surgical, zero downtime, lasting results.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-5">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Realistic follicle dot pattern</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Covers thinning, alopecia &amp; scars</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>2–3 sessions recommended</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$650</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">3 hr / session</p></div><a href="/book/" data-service-id="scalp-micropigmentation" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300">
          <div class="relative h-52 overflow-hidden"><img src="/images/lip-neutralization-treatment.jpg" alt="Lip neutralization permanent makeup pigment correction" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div></div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-2">Lip Neutralization</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">Correct dark, uneven, or discolored lip pigmentation before adding lip blush or other permanent makeup. Uses precise pigment theory to balance underlying tones for a clean, even base.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-5">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Corrects dark, purple &amp; uneven lip tone</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Prepares lips for lip blush or color work</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Consultation before treatment</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$399</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">2 hr / session</p></div><a href="/book/" data-service-id="lip-neutralization" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300">
          <div class="relative h-52 overflow-hidden"><img src="/images/lip-blush-treatment.jpg" alt="Lip blush semipermanent makeup pigmentation treatment" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div></div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-2">Lip Blush</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">Enhance your natural lip color and definition with a soft, blended pigment deposit. Adds shape, symmetry, and a flush of color that looks effortlessly natural.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-5">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Soft, natural color flush</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Adds definition &amp; symmetry</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Lasts 1–3 years with touch-up</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$499</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">2 hr / session</p></div><a href="/book/" data-service-id="lip-blush" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300">
          <div class="relative h-52 overflow-hidden"><img src="/images/nano-brows-treatment.jpg" alt="Nano brows ultra-fine permanent hair stroke eyebrow technique" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div></div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-2">Nano Brows</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">Ultra-fine, single hair-stroke technique using a digital machine for hyper-realistic, crisp brow strokes. More precise and longer-lasting than microblading.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-5">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Hyper-realistic hair strokes</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Better retention than microblading</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Great for all skin types</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$499</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">2.5 hr / session</p></div><a href="/book/" data-service-id="nano-brows" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300">
          <div class="relative h-52 overflow-hidden"><img src="/images/powder-brows-treatment.jpg" alt="Powder brows ombre shading permanent eyebrow semipermanent makeup" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div></div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-2">Powder Brows</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">Soft, ombré shading that mimics filled-in brow makeup. Ideal for oily skin types and those who prefer a polished, defined look with longer retention.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-5">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Soft powder / ombré finish</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Best for oily &amp; combination skin</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Longer retention than hair strokes</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$549</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">2.5 hr / session</p></div><a href="/book/" data-service-id="powder-brows" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300">
          <div class="relative h-52 overflow-hidden"><img src="/images/custom-semipermanent-makeup.jpg" alt="Custom semipermanent makeup artist professional application" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div></div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-2">Custom Semipermanent Makeup</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">Fully bespoke permanent makeup design. Consultation-based — we'll create a custom treatment plan combining techniques for your unique features and goals.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-5">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Tailored technique combination</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Consultation before any work begins</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Final price confirmed after consultation</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">From $450</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">2 hr · pricing after consult</p></div><a href="/book/" data-service-id="custom-semipermanent-makeup" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-10 bg-neutral-50 border-t border-neutral-100">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-400 mb-4">Also Explore</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="/services/facials/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-full text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:border-primary-300 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Facials</a>
        <a href="/services/advanced-treatments/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-full text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:border-primary-300 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Advanced Treatments</a>
        <a href="/services/ancillary/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-full text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:border-primary-300 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Ancillary Services</a>
        <a href="/services/lash-brow-body/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-full text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:border-primary-300 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Lash, Brow &amp; Body</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14 bg-neutral-900 text-white text-center">
    <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif mb-4">Ready to book?</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-400 mb-8">All semipermanent makeup services are standalone bookings. We'll confirm your appointment within 24 hours.</p>
      <a href="/book/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-all font-medium shadow-lg">Request Booking <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"/></svg></a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
